Pilot
Start an assistant-controlled autonomous run without synthetic user follow-up messages.

Usage:
$pilot start [--for <duration>] <goal>
$pilot status
$pilot pause
$pilot resume
$pilot wrap-up
$pilot stop

Examples:
$pilot start --for 4h Improve benchmark accuracy end-to-end
$pilot wrap-up
